It is a containerized kafka cluster using minishift(based on Hortonworks HDF3.2)
Usage:
1. build docker images
  make build
2. import template to minishift
  oc apply -f kafka-cluster-template.yaml
3.open minishift UI, open Catalog page.
  you will see a template "Kafka cluster for HDF3.2"
  click->next->next
  you will see a kafka cluster is created.

